folder: Greenwich Street & Houston Street (West), Manhattan, NY
text:
Greenwich Street, south from West Houston Street as photographed from the uptown "El" platform. Shown are the tracks and station of the 9th Avenue "El" obliterating details of the street below. Buildings shown are on the west side of Greenwich Street. These are mainly warehouses and lofts.

May 7, 1940
Views 1,2

P. L. Sperr

folder: Greenwich Street & Houston Street (West), Manhattan, NY
text:
Greenwich Street, at West Houston Street, showing details of the 9th Avenue "El" station and tracks at this point. The photographer is standing on the downtown platform and is viewing eastward towards that one opposite. Demolition of this structure and its appurtenances is shortly to occur.

June 7, 1940
Views 1,2,3

P. L. Sperr
